text: "Swalla" is a dancehall song by Jason Derulo featuring Nicki Minaj and Ty Dolla Sign, released on February 24, 2017. The song was originally going to be the first single from Jason Derulo's fifth studio album.https://planetradio.co.uk/hits-radio/entertainment/music/jason-derulo- announces-2018-uk-tour/ Commercially, the song has peaked the top 10 in 23 countries, making it a worldwide success. == References == Category:2017 songs Category:Jason Derulo songs Category:Nicki Minaj songs Category:Dancehall songs
title: Swalla
